(301, 'nerodia', 'floridana', '', 'florida green watersnake', '', '', '', 'squamata', 'snakes', 'north american watersnakes', '', 'serpentes', 'baird and girard', 'goff', '{&quot;1853&quot;:&quot;1936&quot;}', '', 'Elevation of *N. floridana* from a race of *N. cyclopion* is supported by data from Pearson (1966, Bull. Serol. Mus. 36: 8), Lawson (1987, J. Herpetol. 21: 140&ndash;157), and Sanderson (1993, Brimleyana 19: 83&ndash;94). The disjunct populations of *floridana* were examined by Thompson and Crother (1998, Copeia 1998: 715&ndash;719) with allozyme data that revealed no evidence of differentiation.', 'michelle koo', 'Brian I. Crother (Chair), Jeff Boundy, Frank T. Burbrink, Jonathan A. Campbell, R. Alexander Pyron', '2014-12-12', 0, 1, 0),
