(487, 'batrachoseps', 'attenuatus', '', 'california slender salamander', '', '', '', 'caudata', 'salamanders', 'slender salamanders', '', 'caudata', 'bonaparte', 'eschcholtz', '{&quot;1839&quot;:&quot;1833&quot;}', '', 'This species is highly differentiated with respect to mitochondrial DNA and Martin&amp;eacute;z-Solano et al. (2007, Molec. Ecol., 16: 4335 - 4355) recognized five major clades.  Highton (2014, Molec. Phylo. and Evol., 71: 127 - 141), using only the mtDNA data, suggested that as many as 39 species should be recognized.', 'michelle koo', 'Stephen G. Tilley (Chair), Richard Highton, David B. Wake', '', 0, 0, 0),
