(511, 'cryptobranchus', 'alleganiensis', 'bishopi', 'ozark hellbender', '', '', '', 'caudata', 'salamanders', 'hellbenders', '', 'caudata', 'leuckart', 'grobman', '{&quot;1821&quot;:&quot;1943&quot;}', '', 'Collins (1991, Herpet. Rev. 22: 42&ndash;43) elevated this form to species status.  Molecular data presented by Crowhurst et al. (2011, Cons. Genet. 12: 637&ndash;646) are ambiguous with respect to taxonomy.', 'michelle koo', 'Stephen G. Tilley, Richard Highton, David B. Wake', '', 0, 0, 0),
