(568, 'eurycea', 'wallacei', '', 'georgia blind salamander', '', '', '', 'caudata', 'salamanders', 'brook salamanders', '', 'caudata', 'rafinesque', 'carr', '{&quot;1822&quot;:&quot;1939&quot;}', '', 'This taxon was originally placed in the monotypic genus *Haideotriton*. It was considered a junior synonym of *Eurycea* by Dubois (2005, Alytes 23: 20) and shown to nest phylogenetically within *Eurycea* by Pyron and Wiens (2011, Mol. Phylogenet. Evol. 61: 543&ndash;583), and Bonett, et al. (2013 [2014], Evolution 68: 466&ndash;482).', 'michelle koo', 'Stephen G. Tilley (Chair), Richard Highton, David B. Wake', '', 0, 0, 0),
