(684, 'acris', 'blanchardi', '', 'blanchard&amp;#39;s cricket frogs', '', '', '', 'anura', 'frogs', 'cricket frogs', '', 'anura', 'dum', 'harper', '{&quot;1841&quot;:&quot;1947&quot;}', '', 'Gamble et al. (2008, Mol. Phylogenet. Evol. 48: 112&ndash;125) recognized *Acris blanchardi* as distinct from *A. crepitans* on the basis of molecular evidence (and included *Acris crepitans paludicola* as a synonym of *A. blanchardi*), although McCallum and Trauth (2006, Zootaxa 1104: 1&ndash;21) previously rejected the distinctiveness of *A. c. blanchardi* from *A. c. crepitans* on the basis of morphology. Reviewed by Dodd (2013, Frogs U.S. and Canada, 1: 205&ndash;219).', 'michelle koo', 'Darrel R. Frost, David M. Green, Emily Moriarty Lemmon, Roy W. McDiarmid, and Joseph R. Mendelson III', '', 0, 0, 0),
(685, 'acris', 'crepitans', '', 'eastern cricket frog', '', '', '', 'anura', 'frogs', 'cricket frogs', '', 'anura', 'dum', 'baird', '{&quot;1841&quot;:&quot;1854&quot;}', '', 'See comment under *Acris blanchardi*. Reviewed by Gray, Brown, and Blackburn (2005, in Lannoo, M. [ed.],  Amph. Declines: 441&ndash;443), and Dodd (2013, Frogs U.S. and Canada, 1: 219&ndash;226).', 'michelle koo', 'Darrel R. Frost, David M. Green, Emily Moriarty Lemmon, Roy W. McDiarmid, and Joseph R. Mendelson III', '', 0, 0, 0),
(686, 'acris', 'gryllus', '', 'southern cricket frogs', '', '', '', 'anura', 'frogs', 'cricket frogs', '', 'anura', 'dum', 'leconte', '{&quot;1841&quot;:&quot;1825&quot;}', '', 'The lineages delimited on the basis of the molecular evidence of Gamble et al. (2008, Mol. Phylogenet. Evol. 48: 112-125) do not correspond to the nominal subspecies occasionally employed by various previous authors. It seems on that basis that recognition of the subspecies. *A. g. dorsalis* and *A. g. gryllus*, is not warranted.  Reviewed by Jensen (2005, in Lannoo, M. [ed.], Amph. Declines: 443&ndash;444).', 'michelle koo', 'Darrel R. Frost, David M. Green, Emily Moriarty Lemmon, Roy W. McDiarmid, and Joseph R. Mendelson III', '', 0, 0, 0),
(687, 'acris', 'gryllus', 'dorsalis', 'florida cricket frog', '', '', '', 'anura', 'frogs', 'cricket frogs', '', 'anura', 'dum', 'harlan', '{"1841": "1827"}', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', 0, 0, 0),
